      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ONE RACKET (1) rises 110m in distance at her first attempt over the longer trip. Form from this box is sound, including a win. Looks suited here and rates on top. EVIE SCARLETT (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 5 lengths at this track in a handy 34.71 beating Arthur Tango. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. TRUMPET TEARS (3) was in the money last time at this track (41.87) in a OPEN, finishing a 6 length third. Has two wins already from this draw. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. KITTY ANN (8) will have admirers again after placing in a quick run last time out.",
